{"tid":285851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲海面沉船3人墮海 1人不治","createTime":"2017-06-16T07:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T09:56:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b66d1fa52557b45d55e97eb54dd1612783c1c589","tid":285851,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170616/20058195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170616%2F20058195&d=gdRW82Wprm0QCynl%2BG%2BEj%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=dea36425\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170616%2F20058195&h=6a89d7b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170616/20058195</a><br />\n<br />\n長洲海面沉船3人墮海<br />\n1人不治<br />\n<br />\n4,044<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n昨中午12時半左右，一艘漁船在長洲對開海面沉沒，3名男船員墮海，包括1本地男子及2名內地漢。現場消息稱，3人乘坐由南丫島往大陸的漁船<br />\n至長洲對開海面沉船墮海，分別被經過的船家及水警救起，其中1人由水警送往香港仔碼頭再送院搶救，但告不治。<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=gdRW82Wprm0QCynl%2BG%2BEj%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=538e90a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n校巴鏟防撞欄　5車撞3傷<br />\n下一則<br />\n20歲少女將軍澳失蹤　警發相急尋"},{"pid":"ca6750a0c3b29e3925d210da0137913408b86f68","tid":285851,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"係香港人定大陸佬不治？"},{"pid":"41394883e57b4d72277744ff9847ec7f52afbfef","tid":285851,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c8b2214bd650927d47480361a520ff4e4dfabfd","tid":285851,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"oh no"}]}